    "description": "BHIVE Workspace, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Senior Property Advisor for our Visakhapatnam operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout BHIVE Workspace:\nBHIVE Workspace is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with BHIVE Workspace!",
